           <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\"><b>产品</b><b>特点</b>：</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;瓶身采用不含双酚A的新型材料PPSU制造，具有高耐热、高韧度、耐冲击、耐蒸煮等特点。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;奶嘴采用超软液体硅胶制成，厚度是一般奶嘴的两倍，有良好的伸展性，具有母乳喂养的实感。螺旋设计，当乳汁经过时，可有效减少乳汁中的气泡，进而有效的预防宝宝胀气。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;瓶身可耐温180℃，其他部件可耐温120℃，可在水中煮沸消毒。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\"><b>使用方法：</b></span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">使用前将各部件清洗干净并放入水中煮沸消毒3~5分钟。冲调好奶水后，将奶嘴套入螺牙并轻轻拉出，旋上即可使用。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\"><b>爱心提示</b><b>：</b></span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;喂食前必须检查食物温度（较适合的喂奶温度为37℃-42℃）。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;奶瓶须在成人监护下使用，奶嘴不可当玩具或安抚奶嘴使用。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;连续不断的长期吸吮液体会导致蛀牙。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;不要将食品长时间放在奶瓶内，不要直接加热奶瓶内食品。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;请将不用的部件放在宝宝触及不到的地方。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;使用过程中如发现奶瓶或奶嘴等有破裂迹象，请即弃用，另购新品。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">●&nbsp;奶瓶上的刻度为调乳时的大致标准，若需要更精确的计量时，请使用计量杯、量筒等工具。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td height=\"30\" align=\"left\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"90%\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; display: table;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td width=\"150\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">产品质量：</span></td>\r\n                        <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <br />\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\"><strong>问：PPSU奶瓶（瓶身）主要的特点是什么？</strong></span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\"><strong>答：</strong></span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">1：安心材质：不含BPA（双酚A）。无异味。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">2：耐温高：最高耐温可达207℃，连续使用温度也可达180℃。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">3：耐蒸煮：可反复蒸煮消毒，不易产生龟裂现象，因此使用寿命长。</span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px;\">4：高韧度：耐冲击，不易破裂。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1412063232-0.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1412063232-1.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /><img align=\"absMiddle\" alt=\"\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1412063232-2.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-fami